(16, 'Domestic Tour Guidelines', '<p style=\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">IMPORTANT NOTICE -&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 14px; display: inline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Domestic Travel Guidelines</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Some countries have released there own guidelines for indian travellers. Please go through these guidelines carefully before planning your travel, for a hassle free experience.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"travel_inner_ul_text1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 5px 22px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Guidelines for Travel:</li>\r\n	<li class=\"travel_inner_ul_t